行业监管工作的指导意见》。 《指导意见》就进一步加强医疗美容行业监管工作，规范和促进医疗美容行业发展提出一系列针对性举措。 一是坚持保护人民群众生命健康安全底线，明确规定医疗美容服务属于医疗活动，必须遵守卫生健康有关行业准入的法律法规。 二是着重强调跨部门综合监管，在现有法律法规框架下，从登记管理、资质审核、「证」「照」信息共享、通报会商、联合抽查检查、协同监管、行刑衔接等多个维度同时发力，构建贯通协同、高效联动的行业监管体系。 三是统筹监管规范和促进发展，充分考虑医疗美容行业规律特点，在推进优化行业准入条件、提升市场主体登记管理服务、强化信息公开和信用约束等多个方面作出规定。 明确了！「医美」属医疗！十一部门联合发文，市场监管总局最新发声 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4b09110343667821e0bbe08bf1e85c0e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599022658"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izarw2unvp45iEAMaCDk1Mzk2NzgyIJXozaIGMAM47QJAHXIJNTk5MDIyNjU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1683256097.8616064", "card_id": "Q_587490338", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 114}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "智能门锁为何不接交流电？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9b171e41386e209c89738ca4af858339_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587490338"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izarw2unvp45iEAMaCDkyODM0OTQxIKj3iqAGMAg4ugFAHnIJNTg3NDkwMzM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1683256097.8622153", "card_id": "Q_583342136", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《黑豹 2》中瓦甘达科技那么发达了大部分士兵还在使用冷兵器？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "材质再厉害效率肯定也不如热兵器吧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-11deed08d55c8e4e8629c15d8a63a29a_r.jpg?source=54b3c3a5"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": 